{"tid":844700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"厲害了女記者！在英國打鬧　中國封「愛國勇士」","createTime":"2018-10-02T05:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T06:53:46.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e42f6b9cac21f07b4b563ad8f8581e981382002d","tid":844700,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181002/640_ea3930102f93b9c59eeb4982851feb3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181002%2F640_ea3930102f93b9c59eeb4982851feb3d.jpg&h=5a87deec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國央視的女記者孔琳琳在上月30日進入由英國保守黨在伯明罕舉行一場名為「香港自由、法治、自治受損」的座談會，會中孔琳琳突然大鬧會場，還打了上前維安的工作人員，孔琳琳不斷高呼：「我有權利抗議！」、「不要碰我！」而這段影片回到中國，中國網友紛紛「讚許」孔琳琳，更封她為「愛國勇士」。<br />\n<br />\n畫面可見孔琳琳在鬧場之後，有多位工作人員上前維安，還有一名男子抱住孔琳琳，孔琳琳不斷直呼：「不要碰我。」還說：「我有權利抗議。」、「這是民主。」事後孔琳琳所屬的央視指出，孔琳琳提問發言時「表達觀點，竟然遭到百般阻撓，甚至人身侵犯」，並說「任何鼓吹分裂中國的圖謀和行為都是逆歷史潮流和徒勞的」。<br />\n<br />\n不只央視挺自家人，就連中國鄉民也很捧場，紛紛大讚孔琳琳：「堅決維護國家統一，維護祖國尊嚴名譽。」、「支持大妹子，搞笑的是一些軟骨頭懦夫嘲笑一個勇士。」、「孔琳琳好樣的，就是要敢於挑戰這種毫無廉恥的港獨分子！女中豪傑，佩服佩服。」、「沒毛病啊！說人家潑婦的沒素質的，什麼叫有素質？砲彈轟到家門口，還笑呵呵是有素質？在那種場合能讓孔琳琳如此生氣，可見港毒狗說了多麼過分的話。」<br />\n<br />\n但是也有中國網友不認同孔琳琳的「潑婦」形象，認為她是受過高等教育的精英，無論碰到任何問題，至少應該懂得理性的交流與溝通。也有網友批評孔琳琳：「這broken English真的，就是想辯論也是讓人覺得很無力！」、「大吵大鬧，指手畫腳，撒潑打人，沒點素質，真是丟人現眼。」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181002/1439962/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181002%2F1439962%2F&d=GBi8YXmaH8y%2Brevsq%2Fz6V0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a7f7f2b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181002%2F1439962%2F&h=f1bed789\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181002/1439962/</a>"},{"pid":"f7bdebd40adbb2a354def2898123626f80f599cd","tid":844700,"uid":152476,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:36:00.000Z","msg":"踢出境啦"},{"pid":"4d92683ca8fa640f7e1a3e0e71e80b912ef45f11","tid":844700,"uid":126731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"支那賤畜"},{"pid":"dddcafb1732d80c0ce0838cb959984237d0cd854","tid":844700,"uid":61280,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:39:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支那種DNA：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出了蝈才講民主人權示威發惡！！！！</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"924c196c609a0fa5e16c9bd30837820eebcfee03","tid":844700,"uid":213661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:40:39.000Z","msg":"物似主人形"},{"pid":"a5470d8783bbfe98c2811389c8c15bc1f2629dd4","tid":844700,"uid":73849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"成班生蕃仲唔衝去英國唱國歌？<br />\n<br />\nbtw施旖婕報非風化新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1b053fc414f35859fc92fb731a1adf63887b85","tid":844700,"uid":4964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:42:52.000Z","msg":"中國問表達觀點唔得？<br />\n特區政府教我，就算法律上有言論自由，都係可以受到限制架"},{"pid":"af9eb91464bb89aabeb03e61e91ebbb0bd8f1529","tid":844700,"uid":62409,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:42:59.000Z","msg":"「我有權利抗議。」、「這是民主。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a680933adc6e5bab263d92f2e6bc8d1a62ccbc","tid":844700,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:48:25.000Z","msg":"野蠻人入侵"},{"pid":"c6123128fb6f5bf172b88443ab95aa5