replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:29:19.000Z","msg":"唔返支那講同一番話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時唔係趕你出會場咁簡單，監都有得坐呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那人學人講民主言論自由，全世界最冇資格講言論自由就係你哋，你主人話嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0c162736641b7477cbd579b50046d27ab8cbb5","tid":844700,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:48:12.000Z","msg":"係支拿唔敢大聲講既終於有機會發洩出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c93801bf942ca4bd7ca9ce4a03e6c488cfe581","tid":844700,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:50:23.000Z","msg":"有線記者係四川被打時林鄭就叫人守法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19a8fc75503294a548bc756d4e4cebbf4108d25","tid":844700,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:53:46.000Z","msg":"「我有權利抗議。」「這是民主。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n深圳河以北，你夠膽講咩"}]}